@startuml
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #f8fcff
  BorderColor #aaa
}
box "内核缓冲区" #LightCyan
participant KernelBuf
end box
box "用户程序" #LightYellow
participant App
end box

== 【正确做法：ET + 循环读到 EAGAIN】 ==
KernelBuf -> KernelBuf: 收到数据: ABCDEF
App -> KernelBuf: read() → ABCD
note left: 读到数据，继续循环
App -> KernelBuf: read() → EF
note left: 继续循环
App -> KernelBuf: read() → -1 EAGAIN
note left: <color:red>【正确】缓冲区空了，停止</color>

== 【错误做法：ET + 只读一次】 ==
KernelBuf -> KernelBuf: 收到数据: ABCDEF
App -> KernelBuf: read() → ABCD
note left: <color:red>【错误】剩下 EF 永远不会再触发</color>
App -> App: 以为读完了，不再读
KernelBuf -> KernelBuf: EF 永久滞留
@enduml